Request Header

  • # Authorization string required

    The Authorization header must contain the bearer token.

Request Path

  • # foo_id int required

    The id of the Foo to which the Bar belongs.

  • # bar_uuid string required

    The UUID of the Bar to retrieve.

Request Query

  • # q string optional

    The search string.

  • # limit int optional

    The max number of results to return, if not present it will default to 32.

Request Body

  • # F1 string required

  • # F2 string optional

  • # F3 float64 required

  • # F4 float64 optional
